      'Lead technology strategy, architecture, and client delivery.',
      'Offer select freelance engagements in platform engineering and cloud architecture.',
    ],
  },
  {
    title: 'Senior Technical Account Manager',
    company: 'Amazon Web Services (AWS)',
    period: 'Jun 2021 – May 2023',
    location: 'Stockholm, Sweden',
    bullets: [
      'Trusted advisor on Enterprise Support to three of the largest Nordic enterprises.',
      'Owned operational health, cost optimisation and Well-Architected reviews.',
      'Led incident and escalation management for business-critical workloads.',
      'Guided large-scale migration onto EKS, serverless, and IaC.',
    ],
  },
  {
    title: 'Senior DevOps Engineer',
    company: 'ATG (Aktiebolaget Trav och Galopp)',
    period: 'Apr 2019 – May 2021',
    location: 'Stockholm, Sweden',
    bullets: [
