      'Established GitOps delivery model; Splunk and Dynatrace monitoring at 99.999% uptime.',
    ],
  },
  {
    title: 'Solution Architect · Senior Solution Integrator',
    company: 'Ericsson Group',
    period: 'Jul 2011 – Apr 2019',
    location: 'Stockholm / Gurgaon',
    bullets: [
      'Built IT governance framework for a 5G innovation programme.',
      'Designed API layer and north/southbound interfaces in Go and Python within Docker/Kubernetes.',
      'Represented Ericsson at IBC and Mobile World Congress as demo engineer.',
    ],
  },
  {
    title: 'Team Lead, IPTV Operations',
    company: 'Alcatel-Lucent Managed Services',
    period: '2010 – 2011',
    location: '—',
    bullets: ['Led IPTV operations and managed service delivery for enterprise clients.'],
  },
  {
